## Enterprise Funnel Platform: Full Technical Specification for Codex

> **Purpose**: This document is the SOLE BUILD REFERENCE for Codex/Cursor. Every section contains implementation-ready specifications with exact data schemas, component APIs, state management patterns, and rendering logic. NO section is marketing copy.
>
> **Target**: Clone + exceed ConvertFlow + Unbounce + Instapage + Leadpages capabilities
> **Stack**: React 18 + Convex + Tailwind CSS + Slate.js + Preact (published pages)
> **Repo**: `rtmendes/offer-engine-v3` (Viktor Space)

