## 1. SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

### 1.1 High-Level Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    OFFER ENGINE v3                           │
├──────────────┬──────────────┬──────────────┬───────────────┤
│   Builder    │  Published   │   Analytics  │  Admin/API    │
│   (React)    │  (Preact)    │  (Convex)    │  (Convex)     │
├──────────────┴──────────────┴──────────────┴───────────────┤
│                    Convex Backend                           │
│  ┌─────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬────────────┐ │
│  │ Pages   │ Contacts │ Events   │ Segments │ Experiments│ │
│  │ Blocks  │ Sessions │ Goals    │ Rules    │ Variants   │ │
│  │ Styles  │ Fields   │ Actions  │ Triggers │ Splits     │ │
│  └─────────┴──────────┴──────────┴──────────┴────────────┘ │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│              Edge CDN (Vercel/Cloudflare)                    │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │ Published pages: Static HTML + hydration islands     │   │
│  │ Tracking script: Identity resolution + events        │   │
│  │ A/B split: Server-side variant assignment            │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 1.2 Frontend Architecture (Builder App)

```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── App.tsx                    # Root router
│   ├── layouts/
│   │   ├── DashboardLayout.tsx    # Sidebar + topbar + content
│   │   └── BuilderLayout.tsx      # Full-screen builder (no sidebar)
│   └── routes/
│       ├── dashboard/             # Overview, stats
│       ├── pages/                 # Landing pages CRUD
│       ├── popups/                # Popup CTAs
│       ├── sticky-bars/           # Sticky bar CTAs
│       ├── embeds/                # Embedded CTAs
│       ├── campaigns/             # Multi-step campaigns
│       ├── quizzes/               # Quiz funnels
│       ├── contacts/              # Contact database
│       ├── segments/              # Audience segments
│       ├── experiments/           # A/B tests
│       ├── insights/              # Analytics
│       ├── broadcasts/            # Email/notification sends
│       ├── templates/             # Template library
│       ├── integrations/          # 3rd party connections
