### 1.3 Backend Architecture (Convex)

```
convex/
├── schema.ts                      # Full database schema (see Section 2)
├── pages.ts                       # Page CRUD + versioning
├── blocks.ts                      # Block CRUD within pages
├── templates.ts                   # Template library
├── contacts.ts                    # Contact/lead management
├── segments.ts                    # Audience segmentation
├── experiments.ts                 # A/B testing logic
├── analytics.ts                   # Event ingestion + aggregation
├── identity.ts                    # Identity resolution
├── campaigns.ts                   # Campaign orchestration
├── forms.ts                       # Form submission handling
├── quizzes.ts                     # Quiz logic + scoring
├── integrations.ts                # 3rd party webhooks/APIs
├── publishing.ts                  # Page publish pipeline
├── domains.ts                     # Custom domain management
├── media.ts                       # File/image uploads (Convex storage)
├── broadcasts.ts                  # Email/notification sends
├── ai.ts                          # Remix AI generation
├── crons.ts                       # Scheduled jobs (analytics rollup, experiment eval)
├── http.ts                        # HTTP routes (published pages, tracking pixel, webhooks)
└── _generated/                    # Auto-generated Convex types
```

