## 13-17. ADDITIONAL SYSTEMS (Summary Specs)

### 13. Form System
- Server-side validation (Convex mutation)
- Field-level validation rules (regex, min/max, required, custom)
- Conditional fields (show field B only if field A = X)
- Multi-step forms (step 1 → step 2 → step 3)
- File upload fields (Convex storage)
- Hidden fields (UTM capture, referrer, page URL)
- Double opt-in flow (send verification email → confirm → add to list)
- Honeypot + rate limiting for spam prevention
- Integration triggers on submit (GHL, Mailchimp, Klaviyo, Zapier webhook)

### 14. Quiz Funnel Engine
- 4 quiz types: scored, branching, personality, product recommendation
- Question types: single choice, multiple choice, image choice, slider, text, rating, NPS
- Branching logic: answer → next question (skip logic)
- Scoring: per-answer points, score ranges → results
- Result pages: custom content per result, product recommendations
- Lead capture gate: before or after results (or none for anonymous)
- Progress bar: bar, steps, fraction display
- Analytics: completion rate, drop-off per question, answer distribution

### 15. Popup & Sticky Bar System
- Trigger types: immediate, delay (X seconds), scroll % (25/50/75/100), exit intent, click element, inactivity timer
- Display frequency: every visit, once/session, once/day, once/week, once ever (cookie-based)
- Position: center modal, slide-in (4 corners), full screen, top bar, bottom bar
- Close behavior: X button, backdrop click, ESC key
- Animation: fade, slide, zoom, bounce
- URL targeting: show on specific pages (contains, equals, regex)
- Device targeting: desktop only, mobile only, all
- Audience targeting: segment-based
- A/B testing integration: test different popup variants
- Analytics: impressions, closes, conversions, dismissal rate

### 16. Campaign Orchestration
- Multi-step funnel builder (visual pipeline editor)
- Step types: landing page, popup, email, SMS, delay, condition, webhook
- Conditional routing: branch based on form answers, quiz results, segment membership
- GHL pipeline sync: map funnel steps → GHL pipeline stages
- Funnel analytics: entry → step completion → drop-off → final conversion
- Revenue attribution: track $ per funnel step
- Automated emails: trigger on step entry, delay, condition
- Webhook actions: hit external APIs on step transitions

### 17. Integration Layer
- GHL (GoHighLevel): Contact sync, pipeline management, opportunity creation, form → GHL workflow trigger
- Shopify: Product catalog sync, cart events, order tracking, customer matching
- Stripe: Checkout sessions, subscription management, revenue tracking
- Email platforms: Mailchimp, Klaviyo, ConvertKit, ActiveCampaign, Drip — list management, tag sync, campaign triggers
- Webhook (generic): POST/PUT to any URL with field mapping
- Zapier: Webhook trigger for 5000+ app connections
- Slack: Notification on form submit, conversion, experiment winner
- GA4: Event forwarding (Measurement Protocol)
- Meta Pixel: Event forwarding (Conversions API)
- Google Tag Manager: Data layer push

