## 18. DOMAIN & HOSTING SYSTEM

```typescript
// Custom domain flow:
// 1. User adds domain "fgs.wantthisoffer.com" in settings
// 2. System generates CNAME record instruction: fgs.wantthisoffer.com → cname.vercel-dns.com
// 3. User adds DNS record
// 4. System verifies DNS (polling every 30s for 5 min)
// 5. SSL auto-provisioned via Vercel
// 6. Page routing: domain + slug → page lookup → serve published HTML

// URL structure:
// {domain}/p/{slug}     → published landing page
// {domain}/quiz/{slug}  → published quiz
// {domain}/thanks       → thank you page
// Custom paths supported (user-defined routing rules)

// Fallback: If no custom domain, pages served from:
// offers.insightprofit.live/p/{slug}
```

