## 20. AI FEATURES — REMIX ENGINE

```typescript
// AI-powered page generation from text prompt
// Uses free-tier models (Cerebras Qwen3-235B) for cost optimization

interface RemixRequest {
  prompt: string;                // "Create a lead gen page for a fitness coaching program"
  templateBase: string | null;   // Start from existing template
  brand: {
    name: string;
    colors: { primary: string; secondary: string; accent: string };
    fonts: { heading: string; body: string };
    logo: string | null;
  };
  pageType: string;              // "landing_page", "popup", etc.
  industry: string | null;
  tone: string | null;           // "professional", "casual", "urgent", "luxury"
}

// AI generates:
// 1. Page structure (which blocks, in what order)
// 2. Copy for each block (headings, body, CTAs)
// 3. Color scheme adjustments
// 4. Image suggestions (stock photo keywords or AI-generated)
// 5. Form fields appropriate for the use case

// Token cost: ~2,000 tokens per page generation
// Using Cerebras Qwen3-235B: $0 (free tier)
// Fallback: Together.ai Qwen3-235B: ~$0.002 per page
```

