## 22. PERFORMANCE TARGETS

```
Published page metrics:
├── First Contentful Paint:  < 0.8s
├── Largest Contentful Paint: < 1.2s
├── Time to Interactive:      < 1.5s
├── Total Blocking Time:      < 100ms
├── Cumulative Layout Shift:  < 0.05
├── Page weight:              < 200KB (HTML + CSS + tracking JS)
├── Hydration JS:             < 20KB gzipped (only for interactive blocks)
└── Lighthouse score:         > 95

Builder app metrics:
├── Initial load:             < 2s
├── Block add/delete:         < 50ms
├── Drag and drop:            60fps
├── Auto-save:                < 500ms
├── Undo/redo:                < 50ms
└── Preview render:           < 200ms
```

